description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - This 4-video pack contains a series of exercises to help you develop fluency improvising in a melodic way. By focusing on the "pretty notes", or upper extensions - 9ths, 11ths, and 13ths - and connecting them melodically, your solos will take on a whole new level of beauty and harmonic complexity, and you'll be able to navigate difficult chord progressions with ease. A powerful set of tools for any instrument! (Level: Intermediate)
title: Geoffrey Keezer - "Pretty Notes" (Preview)
